INSERT INTO `mac_vod` VALUES('19972','大仙衙门','','daxianyamen','D','','http://puui.qpic.cn/vcover_vt_pic/0/in61eduxel9asc4t1465993831.jpg/220','http://puui.qpic.cn/vcover_vt_pic/0/in61eduxel9asc4t1465993831.jpg/220','','王传君 吴倩 陈奕 金梦阳子 房鹿 张晓晨 斯琴高丽 何明翰 马莉 徐震 郭晓峰 佟梦实','蓝志伟','同房不同床,恶作剧,男女','','大陆','国语','0','12','',',1168,','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','227163','0','0','0','0','0','0','10.0','0','367','1481739650','1481872635','0','0','王元丰出身官宦世家，不爱钱财名利、不谙男女风月，却对解谜破案情有独钟。王元丰无意中救了被封印的狐仙小翠。小翠为报恩，嫁给他为妻。王元丰不开窍，不近女色，故两人同房不同床。小翠古灵精怪，常与元丰胡闹，让王母头疼不已。不料小翠的恶作剧，却阴差阳错帮助王家躲过王给谏的陷害，并且整治了贪官。王元丰因此得到百姓拥戴，当上县令。他为官正直清廉，在小翠的帮助下，破了很多奇案，百姓们称之为“大仙衙门”。好景不长，小翠因为时限已到，终究人狐殊途，离开元丰。深爱小翠的元丰失落病倒，小翠不忍，施法让元丰忘了自己，爱上钟氏女。一天，元丰偶然打开珍藏的画像，才想起从前小翠的样子，潸然泪下。\n        ','qq','','','01$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/in61eduxel9asc4/r0020zxyz78.html#02$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/in61eduxel9asc4/f00205ospck.html#03$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/in61eduxel9asc4/a0020pspma2.html#04$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/in61eduxel9asc4/v0020899njd.html#05$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/in61eduxel9asc4/y0020ulg0qt.html#06$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/in61eduxel9asc4/s0020qq9c68.html#07$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/in61eduxel9asc4/d0020gsq7tb.html#08$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/in61eduxel9asc4/x002050bmzs.html#09$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/in61eduxel9asc4/f0020nj4mw2.html#10$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/in61eduxel9asc4/w0020gx9xuf.html#11$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/in61eduxel9asc4/m00207muyzr.html#12$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/in61eduxel9asc4/a0020rjbbo7.html#13$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/in61eduxel9asc4/b0020hlhupx.html#14$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/in61eduxel9asc4/v0020ndspxd.html#15$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/in61eduxel9asc4/f0020mrsz8t.html#16$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/in61eduxel9asc4/r0020kwkpae.html#17$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/in61eduxel9asc4/r0020fce2kf.html#18$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/in61eduxel9asc4/p0020muoabl.html#19$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/in61eduxel9asc4/i00200ywlkj.html#20$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/in61eduxel9asc4/i0020zpys31.html#21$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/in61eduxel9asc4/r00207vwytc.