INSERT INTO `mac_vod` VALUES('20010','老马家的幸福往事','','laomajiadexingfuwangshi','L','','http://puui.qpic.cn/vcover_vt_pic/0/j6y2cprl3bynx3lt1458054114.jpg/220','http://puui.qpic.cn/vcover_vt_pic/0/j6y2cprl3bynx3lt1458054114.jpg/220','','林永健 何赛飞 辛柏青 陈紫函 陈洁 涂松岩 于和伟 六月 王菁华 吴秀波 李光洁','杨文军','上海电视节,算命先生,白玉兰,杨文军,改革开放','','大陆','国语','0','12','',',1000,','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','91403','0','0','0','0','0','0','8.0','0','491','1481739675','1482086401','0','0','不幸被算命先生言中，相貌平平的马一毛（林永建 饰）从父辈起就过着颠沛流离的生活，早年间在广东干过各种上得或上不得台面的营生，后来总算在上海的弄堂里落脚，娶得漂亮的妻子胡根娣（何赛飞 饰），并育有三个子女：马鸣、马风和马拉。从文革十年到改革开放，老马一家经历了风风雨雨，而许是遗传了马家无法安定的基因，他们的孩子成年后也相继离家，四下闯荡世界。他们来来往往，经历了心灵和身体上的创痛与洗礼，寻找着生而为人的真意，寻找着属于自己最为本初的幸福……\n本片荣获第17届上海电视节白玉兰奖最佳导演奖（杨文军）。\n        ','qq','','','01$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/j6y2cprl3bynx3l/j0020b8v2jw.html#02$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/j6y2cprl3bynx3l/a0020ve58ot.html#03$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/j6y2cprl3bynx3l/n0020frl7uy.html#04$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/j6y2cprl3bynx3l/l0020y0ztrp.html#05$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/j6y2cprl3bynx3l/c0020xoioru.html#06$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/j6y2cprl3bynx3l/n0020aab931.html#07$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/j6y2cprl3bynx3l/q0020xyylzy.html#08$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/j6y2cprl3bynx3l/q00209tipn9.html#09$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/j6y2cprl3bynx3l/v0020pk9bic.html#10$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/j6y2cprl3bynx3l/v00207bamq9.html#11$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/j6y2cprl3bynx3l/y0020etsyms.html#12$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/j6y2cprl3bynx3l/l00200ec090.html#13$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/j6y2cprl3bynx3l/w0020z9q2cv.html#14$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/j6y2cprl3bynx3l/d0020vesyn0.html#15$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/j6y2cprl3bynx3l/x0020lj4wfa.html#16$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/j6y2cprl3bynx3l/h0020tph4qy.html#17$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/j6y2cprl3bynx3l/b0020zlxmh3.html#18$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/j6y2cprl3bynx3l/b00206lqxvk.html#19$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/j6y2cprl3bynx3l/x0020tyqfiu.html#20$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/j6y2cprl3bynx3l/u0020w69lul.html#21$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/j6y2cprl3bynx3l/b0020oslgmq.html#22$http