INSERT INTO `mac_vod` VALUES('20043','红色黎明','','hongseliming','H','','http://puui.qpic.cn/vcover_vt_pic/0/sesj1yzulmp76b9t1461760341.jpg/220','http://puui.qpic.cn/vcover_vt_pic/0/sesj1yzulmp76b9t1461760341.jpg/220','','朱雨辰 杨雪 夏雨 张戈 舒耀瑄 刘雨鑫 王佳宁 殷飞 龙胜男','徐宗政','三大战役,中国历史,人民解放军,落下帷幕,国民党','','大陆','国语','0','12','',',965,','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','336993','0','0','0','0','0','0','10.0','0','391','1481739705','1482086436','0','0','故事发生在决定中国历史走向的1949年，恢弘壮伟的三大战役相继落下帷幕，中国人民解放军在四万万人民的支持下取得了解放战争的胜利。共产党邀请国民党代表前往北平和谈，以尽可能减少对百姓的荼毒和伤害。而在和谈的表象下，国军方面则紧锣密鼓备战，企图划江而治，分庭抗礼。位于江西的古城梓溪狼悚山，既是国民党的势力范围，也是一个土匪猖獗的凶险所在。土匪头子贺云峰（朱雨辰 饰）在山头林立的江湖中左右搏杀，风头正劲，在结拜兄弟保安司令郑国忠（林熙越 饰）的支持下更成为不可小觑的一方霸主。意外的邂逅，彻底改变了贺云峰和郑国忠的命运。贺偶然救助了共产党陈子墨（杨雪 饰），由此和郑发生裂痕。\n而随着新中国建立后的大势所趋，这些江湖中人都将面临重大的抉择……\n        ','qq','','','01$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/sesj1yzulmp76b9/u0021ljnyds.html#02$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/sesj1yzulmp76b9/g00218gd3an.html#03$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/sesj1yzulmp76b9/h0021n1fmlg.html#04$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/sesj1yzulmp76b9/t0021prunms.html#05$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/sesj1yzulmp76b9/f00216sh56o.html#06$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/sesj1yzulmp76b9/e0021r94u0u.html#07$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/sesj1yzulmp76b9/i0021rbisdu.html#08$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/sesj1yzulmp76b9/c0021xvo1sl.html#09$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/sesj1yzulmp76b9/a0021qcgikd.html#10$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/sesj1yzulmp76b9/u0021ryxmb9.html#11$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/sesj1yzulmp76b9/r0021xrsear.html#12$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/sesj1yzulmp76b9/x0021dudatg.html#13$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/sesj1yzulmp76b9/m00218vge2t.html#14$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/sesj1yzulmp76b9/v00218py8mv.html#15$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/sesj1yzulmp76b9/a0021llgia7.html#16$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/sesj1yzulmp76b9/q0021nhggmo.html#17$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/sesj1yzulmp76b9/h0021yqi4tu.html#18$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/sesj1yzulmp76b9/h002170hfi4.html#19$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/sesj1yzulmp76b9/k0021cb1jcf.html#20$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/sesj1yzulmp76b9/o0021v5b8q8.html#21$http://v.qq.com/x