INSERT INTO `mac_vod` VALUES('20134','幸福最晴天','','xingfuzuiqingtian','X','','http://puui.qpic.cn/vcover_vt_pic/0/ii2aanebq5dpp1st1458063259.jpg/220','http://puui.qpic.cn/vcover_vt_pic/0/ii2aanebq5dpp1st1458063259.jpg/220','','贺军翔 张钧甯 周子涵 李易峰 郑伟 廖慧珍 马利欧','徐辅军','安徽卫视,幸福最晴天,幸福三颗星,学会生存,浪漫爱情','','大陆','国语','0','13','',',183,','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','157068','0','0','0','0','0','0','9.0','0','70','1481771326','1482344245','0','0','平凡女孩方咏咏（张钧甯饰）自小便学会生存之道，号称“万能小姐”。一日上班路上，咏咏与年轻有为的企业巨子项允杰（贺军翔饰）相遇，两人不打不相识。育幼院拆迁事件，让允杰的弟弟项允超（李易峰饰）邂逅纯真乐观的咏咏，深为其所动。因缘巧合，咏咏阴错阳差地几次撞见允杰，两人擦出火花。小男孩小念突然闯进了允杰的世界，原来他就是允杰与前妻汪岚（周子涵饰）当年所生的孩子。然而就是在小念的意外牵引下，允杰与咏咏开始互相了解，彼此信任。一场交织爱恨情仇的浪漫对决由此展开。\n25集青春都市浪漫爱情偶像剧《幸福最晴天》，由贺军翔、张钧甯、李易峰、周子涵等俊男美女领衔主演。本剧集是安徽卫视自制偶像剧“幸福三部曲”的第二部，另外两部分别是《幸福一定强》和《幸福三颗星》。\n        ','qq','','','01$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/ii2aanebq5dpp1s/c0020c4zt6a.html#02$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/ii2aanebq5dpp1s/x002024dw0g.html#03$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/ii2aanebq5dpp1s/n00205rzw1r.html#04$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/ii2aanebq5dpp1s/s00203u4m0c.html#05$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/ii2aanebq5dpp1s/l00202japzr.html#06$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/ii2aanebq5dpp1s/m0020f5j6uf.html#07$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/ii2aanebq5dpp1s/j00200oyu1g.html#08$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/ii2aanebq5dpp1s/h0020yyg0t9.html#09$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/ii2aanebq5dpp1s/p0020s9ym2f.html#10$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/ii2aanebq5dpp1s/l0020cno0lm.html#11$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/ii2aanebq5dpp1s/g00207ijh77.html#12$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/ii2aanebq5dpp1s/i0020ovk6vf.html#13$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/ii2aanebq5dpp1s/h0020ukdtis.html#14$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/ii2aanebq5dpp1s/m0020wxi4sl.html#15$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/ii2aanebq5dpp1s/d0020futiq4.html#16$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/ii2aanebq5dpp1s/w0020m1jkw1.html#17$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/ii2aanebq5dpp1s/r0020vgec76.html#18$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/ii2aanebq5dpp1s/r0020ns0l3c.html#19$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/ii2aanebq5dpp1s/t0020em0ju2.html#20$http://v.qq.com/x/cover/ii2aanebq5dpp1s/v0020uxhsy8.html#21$http://v.qq.